Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bulle-Triceratops!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Suplex!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Captain were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else can we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Predator's Trap -\NBlack Maria's Temptation"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've attempted to kill you\Ncountless times,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:04:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I've been struck down countless times!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I became stronger thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kept me on the island\Nwasn't only those handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't fight for this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't call myself Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your whole body is so tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you got a cut on your stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will end you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franken-Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V-for-Victory Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice try, you stupid robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will end {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I'm not good with swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's come to this,\NI'll use the strongest game-changing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you run?! Shame on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up close to the Performance Floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't let this guy reach it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bulle-Triceratops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaon Cannon, Portable Version!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The symbol of terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Animal Kingdom Pirates' Tobi Roppo!\NDon't mess with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you down with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mag... num-ceratops!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky Radical Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dog-Dog Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Type!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Model Okuchi-no-Makami.\NIt's a valuable Mythical Type fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a guardian deity of the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it was eaten by someone\Nwho calls himself Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing but a blunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the Land of Wano for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a guardian deity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochi had a talent for exploitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country is a weapon factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dominate it by forcing its people to labor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kozuki Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open the borders of Land of Wano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...free them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be unleashed on the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namuji Glacier Fang!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you open the borders!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's not just fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W... W...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worms?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's a long shot,\Nbut I'll ask you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:13:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get home,\NI don't want you to tell anyone about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was too easy. She'll definitely tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie! There's no way\Nthat a child can keep a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell\Nbecause I'm not interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dereshi"? What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a funny girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're cute when you laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazingly, you scored 100% on the exam\Nfor the doctoral degree you took the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today on, you can introduce yourself\Nas an archaeologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Clover...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've become\Na fine archaeologist, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you my mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I've left you alone\Nfor a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:14:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, Robin-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To sea? So you wanna set out to sea, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom has been busy with her\Narchaeological research all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when she comes back\Nto this island next time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask her\Nto take me with her to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I studied hard and I was finally\Nable to become an archaeologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An archaeologist?\NWhen you're still so small?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even remember\Nyour mom's face, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... but she's still my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Saul...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that the world has a blank history\Nof 100 years that no one knows about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that my mom is traveling\Naround the world investigating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could it mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that she's traveling in search of\Nthose stones called Ponegliffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you know about Ponegliffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin... Do you know your mom's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Olvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Olvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Robin is Olvia's daughter...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then could this place be...\Nan island called Ohara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be\Nsitting around talking! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might shock you,\Nbut listen to me carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy battleships should be\Nheaded to Ohara right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to eliminate\Nthe scholars on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:18:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin... You fool!\NYou shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you my mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you my mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're confusing me\Nwith someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've grown, but don't you remember me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you\Nto return all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it for me. I got caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Set out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! There's no one on the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alone now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll meet friends someday for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is vast, so someday, definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll come across friends\Nwho'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is born\Ninto this world to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're having a hard time,\NI taught you what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illusion Mist...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet memories ruin you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. This is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This illusion is a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mirror that reflects my childish heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when my friends are fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just indulge in my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul wouldn't say such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,History is the treasure of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll certainly light up the future\Nwe'll live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people can't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tres Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freesia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come the Illusion Mist...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come it didn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.62,0:22:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Robin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to hold my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.09,0:22:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and walk with me someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.17,0:22:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I studied hard and\Nwas able to become an archaeologist!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.18,0:22:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can read Ponegliffs, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live, Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.59,0:23:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...alongside my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Rumbar Pirates appear in the heavy mist!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It evokes the voice of an old friend, Laboon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.52,0:23:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seeing his old buddies confuses Brook!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their blades come to attack him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A tragedy that shouldn't be possible\Nterrifies Brook's mind!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Slash the Nightmare - Brook Draws His Freezing Sword!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
